%F A395594 a(n) = (9*F(n/2) + F((n/2)-1))^2 if n is even and (9*F((n-1)/2) + F(((n-1)/2)-1))*(9*F((n-1)/2+1)+F((n-1)/2)) if n is odd where F(n) = Fibonacci(n).
